HEADWORD: Arcual
<hw>Arc"u*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
an arc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Arcual measure of an angle</b></col> <fld>(Math.)</fld>,
<cd>that in which the unit angle has its measuring arc equal to the
radius of the circle.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

